headline: WM Earnings Miss Estimates in Q3, Revenues Appreciate 15% Y/Y
summary: WM's third-quarter 2025 results fall short of estimates despite a 15% y/y revenue jump, lifted by strong landfill and renewable energy gains.

headline: Why Waste Management (WM) Stock Is Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of waste management services provider Waste Management (NYSE:WM) fell 3.8% in the morning session after the company reported third-quarter results that missed Wall Street's expectations for both revenue and earnings per share.
